327
00:22:53,120 --> 00:22:54,951
Pinjam saja, deh.
Sampai nanti bisa beli sendiri.

328
00:22:56,040 --> 00:22:56,995
Yeah.

329
00:22:57,080 --> 00:22:58,752
Jangan sampai hilang.

